title: South-Facing, Euro-Style One-Bedroom at Parkway West
posting_body: ['Property Address', '4556 46th Avenue S - 310 | Minneapolis, MN 55406', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Available 10/1:', 'Stunning, Euro-Style 1BR in the Longfellow Neighborhood!', 'This charming South-facing one-bedroom apartment home features a spacious and open great room, a Euro-style kitchen with tile backsplash, a full set of appliances, and a movable center island.', 'You will enjoy the peace and quiet of the embedded bedroom and you will be in awe of the great natural light and the pretty view that is offered into the Minnehaha neighborhood!', 'Walk or bike the trails, relax in the park, frequent the shops and meet your friends at the nearby pubs and cafes.', 'The Longfellow neighborhood is always bustling with activity.', 'Parkway West is on the Metro Transit A-Line and just over the Ford Parkway bridge you can enjoy everything the Highland Park neighborhood offers in St. Paul.', 'Your new home is in the middle of everything!', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Final price subject to change pending walk-through inspection.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Fitness Center', 'Community lounge and patio', 'Underground parking', '24 Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Keyless Entry', 'Smoke-Free Building', 'Cat-Friendly', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 718', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,445.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
